<br />\n其餘4名被告李諾文、盧建民、林敖軒及林倫慶則否認所有面對的控罪，包括暴動、非法集結及襲警等罪。 <br />\n<br />\n現時6名被告包括梁天琦、李諾文、盧建文、林傲軒、黃家駒及林倫慶。他們分別被控煽惑暴動、襲警及暴動等共8罪。其中梁天琦被控4項控罪，包括1項煽惑暴動罪、1項襲警罪及2項暴動罪，是本案涉及最多控罪的被告，另外5名被告則涉及暴動、襲警和非法集結等罪。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180122/mobile/bkn-20180122110819877-0122_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180122%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180122110819877-0122_00822_001.html&d=5a%2FMorWabTkAx6%2F7fnF3BQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=419938c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180122/mobile/bkn-20180122110819877-0122_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"954762e0fd11bf00e8ff7bcf4effcf6ada12fa5c","tid":536674,"uid":41658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"家駒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670daf242e551ce5439dc1a45783828271f55196","tid":536674,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:06:55.000Z","msg":"求gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63c61f39c59ebfcc287583d8e3916ad7a26516b","tid":536674,"uid":28503,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:08:04.000Z","msg":"坐監啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞搞陣無幫襯"},{"pid":"f954859a6fb0132df415262de07fad9aaf07043d","tid":536674,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:08:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港共秘密審訊好撚仆街！</span>"},{"pid":"fc093c5dd27045e244cb1ecb2d9b515a611c6d8d","tid":536674,"uid":29090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"邊撚到有襲犬？"},{"pid":"17a2b18cac919a7dd8ccf360ec937ad091a40da7